    <item>
      <title>对冲基金在抛售中削减了 2022 年以来对布伦特原油看涨押注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/hedge-funds-cut-bullish-brent-bets-most-since-2022-amid-selloff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在算法抛售和对需求的担忧加剧的背景下，对冲基金对布伦特原油的看涨押注大幅减少，降幅为近两年来最大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/hedge-funds-cut-bullish-brent-bets-most-since-2022-amid-selloff</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 20:14:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>派拉蒙在 Skydance 收购文件争夺战中占据优势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/paramount-global-gains-edge-in-fight-over-skydance-buyout-files</link>
      <description><![CDATA[派拉蒙全球公司 (Paramount Global) 准备拒绝向养老基金移交内部文件的要求，该要求引发了人们对该公司被天舞传媒 (Skydance Media) 以 24 亿美元收购的质疑，此次收购将这家著名好莱坞影业公司的控制权转移给制片人大卫·埃里森 (David Ellison)。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/paramount-global-gains-edge-in-fight-over-skydance-buyout-files</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 19:32:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>就业数据增强美联储降息预期，美元或创今年最大单日跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/dollar-s-worst-day-this-year-shows-fed-bets-outweigh-haven-bid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美元出现自五月以来的最大跌幅，因美国劳动力报告意外疲软，加剧了人们对经济前景的担忧，导致交易员押注美联储今年将更积极地降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/dollar-s-worst-day-this-year-shows-fed-bets-outweigh-haven-bid</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 15:53:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纳斯达克 100 指数进入调整区间，人工智能宠儿股价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/nasdaq-100-is-in-correction-territory-with-ai-darlings-sinking</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大型科技公司的剧烈轮动导致纳斯达克 100 指数陷入回调区域，短短三周内市值蒸发逾 2 万亿美元，交易员平仓了一年多来获利颇丰的头寸。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/nasdaq-100-is-in-correction-territory-with-ai-darlings-sinking</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 13:47:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>华尔街施压美联储放松政策 国债价格飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/treasury-two-year-yields-fall-to-14-month-low-on-fed-cut-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国就业数据走软引发人们对美联储将开始大幅降息以防止经济停滞的猜测，美国国债市场周五加速上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/treasury-two-year-yields-fall-to-14-month-low-on-fed-cut-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 00:41:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：标普 500 指数迎来 2022 年 10 月以来最糟糕的就业形势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[疲软的就业报告引发人们担忧，美联储维持利率在二十年高位的决定可能会导致经济进一步放缓，从而加剧了股市抛售，债券收益率下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 22:41:21 GMT</pubDate>
